msgid "Thank you for your interest in participating in the `Google Summer of Code program <https://summerofcode.withgoogle.com/>`__ with the `Qubes OS team <https://www.qubes-os.org/team/>`__. You can read more about the Google Summer of Code program at the `official website <https://summerofcode.withgoogle.com/>`__ and the `official FAQ <https://developers.google.com/open-source/gsoc/faq>`__."
